content.p: Academic life forms the core of your university experience, but we know that campus life and student services are important too. If you'd like to feedback to us about non-academic matters such as safety, sports facilities, IT facilities, accommodation and more, we invite you to check out our Student experience survey or get in touch with the Campus Services Committee. telephone: +6 (03) 8924 8000 fax: +6 (03) 8924 8001
